\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
displays the help message and exits
.TP
\fB\-v\fR, \fB\-\-verbose\fR
supresses quiet flag and sets verbose flag
.TP
\fB\-V\fR, \fB\-\-version\fR
print version info

